>> title: Curry Rice Bowl
>> cuisine: Indian
>> tags: bowl, quick-assembly, vegan, gluten-free, soy-free
>> servings: 1

-- Assembly time: 5 minutes

Add @../components/grains/coconut-basmati-rice{1%cup} as base in #bowl{}.

Heat @../components/proteins/coconut-chickpea-curry{1%cup} and add to bowl.

Add @../components/vegetables/curry-roasted-vegetables{1/2%cup}.

Drizzle @../components/sauces/tikka-style-sauce{1%tbsp} over top.

Add @coconut yogurt{2%tbsp} dollop.

Garnish with @fresh cilantro{1%tbsp}.

-- A warming, aromatic bowl
